/char> faveur <char style="w" strong="H5927">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H1961">mon</char> bien-aimé, <char style="w" strong="H5927">et</char> qui fait parler <char style="w" strong="H5927">les</char> lèvres <char style="w" strong="H5927">de</char> ceux qui dorment. <verse eid="SNG 7:9" /><verse number="10" style="v" sid="SNG 7:10" />Je suis <char style="w" strong="H1980">à</char> mon bien-aimé, <char style="w" strong="H2896">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H1980">son</char> désir tend vers moi. <verse eid="SNG 7:10" /><verse number="11" style="v" sid="SNG 7:11" />Viens, mon bien-aimé, sortons aux champs, passons <char style="w" strong="H5921">la</char> nuit aux villages. <verse eid="SNG 7:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="SNG 7:12" />Levons-nous <char style="w" strong="H3318">le</char> matin <char style="w" strong="H3318">pour</char> <char style="w" strong="H3212">aller</char> <char style="w" strong="H3318">aux</char> vignes; <char style="w" strong="H3212">et</char> voyons si <char style="w" strong="H3318">la</char> vigne <char style="w" strong="H1730">est</char> avancée, <char style="w" strong="H3212">et</char> si <char style="w" strong="H3318">la</char> grappe <char style="w" strong="H1730">est</char> formée, <char style="w" strong="H3212">et</char> si <char style="w" strong="H3318">les</char> grenadiers <char style="w" strong="H7704">sont</char> fleuris; c'est <char style="w" strong="H3318">là</char> <char style="w" strong="H7704">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H3885">je</char> <char style="w" strong="H3212">te</char> donnerai <char style="w" strong="H3212">mes</char> <char style="w" strong="H1730">amours</char>. <verse eid="SNG 7:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="SNG 7:13" /><char style="w" strong="H5414">Les</char> mandragores <char style="w" strong="H5414">exhalent</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">leur</char> odeur, <char style="w" strong="H7200">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">à</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">nos<